{"tid":2294961,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎︱袁國勇強調病毒始於中國：唔敢講太多 驚又俾人鬧","createTime":"2020-11-21T11:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T08:16:01.000Z","uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"97681b2e94986eaf6f1a915c477a057a1cedc986","tid":2294961,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"袁國勇：不相信武肺源自意大利<br />\n<br />\n在嘉賓問答環節中，有嘉賓問及武漢肺災病毒是否源於意大利時，袁指疫情爆發始於中國，而中國的病毒數量最多，指按照科學證據，不相信病毒始於意大利，續指「我唔敢講太多嘢，我驚又俾人鬧」。他續指，內地能夠控制是源於能夠非常高速控制小區市民，反問「係咪可以（香港人）完全唔郁（暫停所有日常生活）？」又強調，公民社會要視乎公民質素，笑言「我哋係一國兩制，所以有齊一國兩制嘅好處同壞處」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/IMBYB3QD65FYHGKN3D3ZSADRIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FIMBYB3QD65FYHGKN3D3ZSADRIY%2F&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM37TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=de140112\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FIMBYB3QD65FYHGKN3D3ZSADRIY%2F&h=1ed68c43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/IMBYB3QD65FYHGKN3D3ZSADRIY/</a>"},{"pid":"c5159a83e978753459fa3f3ae1123708170fa34e","tid":2294961,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T11:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5299d4c3cc5a05764ee47839e2a9ef8c18ef732","tid":2294961,"uid":96091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T11:55:06.000Z","msg":"一陣又分裂國家"},{"pid":"c903ee8df62742288845f9467a3576ed782e3e05","tid":2294961,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T11:55:44.000Z","msg":"佢都話病毒係源於中國果蝠"},{"pid":"9a4c7f274aab7b18e2fcc461c9fae1